divs: sighting detailsmy wife was letting our dog out and noticed a strang anomaly in the sky. she called for me to come quickly to see. i got outside in plenty of time to see the oddly orange\red lit completely noiseless object in the sky. i used a pair of low powered binoculars to see what appeared to have been something in a reverse teardrop shape lit with a noticebly orange light. object was low enough to be a helicopter but moving too fast to be one. my wife and i had no idea what it was. she was glad i actually saw it with her. she couldn't believe what she was seeing.
